cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.SD 

This paper is about data-to-text generation, which is a subfield of natural language processing (NLP) and falls under the category of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also discusses challenges in ensuring data fidelity, which is related to the accuracy of the generated text, and this is a common problem in NLP and machine learning in general. Therefore, the paper could also be categorized under Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The paper also introduces a new dataset and proposes a new method to improve the generation quality, which could fall under Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Software Engineering (cs.SD) respectively.
